text: Dmitriyevka () is a rural locality (a village) in Pervomaysky Selsoviet, Meleuzovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 5 as of 2010. == Geography == It is located 12 km from Meleuz, 5 km from Pervomayskaya. == References == Category:Rural localities in Meleuzovsky District
title: Dmitriyevka, Pervomaysky Selsoviet, Meleuzovsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
